If you see this message, you're running this Shortcut for the first time.

This Shortcut needs to download some necessary files before you could start creating iPad mockups. It will automatically download all required files from a Dropbox directory when you hit OK. These files simply contain all the devices' graphics that the Shortcut needs to generate the mockups – nothing else.

Every time you run MediaKit iPad Mockups the Shortcut will first prompt you to select a screenshot from your photo library. Afterwards you can choose between 34 iPad frames to create your own custom mockups.

———

Thanks for using MediaKit
and don't forget to download 
its other companion Shortcuts.

    &lt;script&gt;
    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");
    
    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';
    
                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }
    &lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;

    &lt;script&gt;
    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");
    
    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';
    
                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }
    &lt;/script&gt;

    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");
    
    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';
    
                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    &lt;script&gt;
    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    &lt;script&gt;
    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    function mockupit() {

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }

    &lt;script&gt;
    var mockup = document.querySelector("#framed");
    var btn = document.querySelector(".button");

    function mockupit() {
        html2canvas(mockup, {
            onrendered: function(canvas) {
                var img = canvas.toDataURL("image/png");
                
                btn.href = img;
                
                document.body.innerHTML = '&lt;h4&gt;Your mockup has been generated.&lt;br&gt;Download it by holding your finger on the image below.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;img class="finalmockup" src="'+img+'"/&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Created with&lt;br&gt;MediaKit™&lt;/h5&gt;';

                    var parent = document.body;
                    var child = document.getElementById("framed");
                    parent.removeChild(child);
            }
        })
    }
    &lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
